{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=193c1e35022232189a9b87def8adf78d&src=http%3A%2F%2Fh.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2F96dda144ad34598275394fbe04f431adcbef846f.jpg","summary":"湖南人文科技学院(Hunan University of Humanities,Science and Technology)位于湖南省湘中新城—娄底市，是一所经国家教育部批准设立的省属公办综合性普通本科高等院校，为硕士学位授予单位。湖南人文科技学院始于1978年创立的娄底师范学校，后来随着历史的发展多次变迁；2004年经教育部批准，学校升格并更名为湖南人文科技学院，成为一所全日制本科普通高校；2010年经国务院学位委员会批准，学校取得硕士学位授予权(服务国家特殊需求人才培养项目)。2017年11月，学校新增为湖南省硕士学位授予单位立项建设单位。截至2018年1月，校园占地面积900亩，校舍建筑面积39万平方米,有15个教学学院，54个本科专业，1个硕士专业学位点，涵盖文、理、工、教、经、管、法、农、艺等九大学科门类。学校面向全国28个省市自治区招生，现有全日制在校生16423人，教职工1149人。","tags":["综合类","本科","公办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"1978","所在地区":"湖南省娄底市氐星路","院校隶属":"湖南省","硕士点":"1"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=47a7cd08e31ee8847636024b1b384a80&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3623786861%2C911931848%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=989d2effac14382646d29d0ae80a885f&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3695844583%2C876900970%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=7c51033d46fc65f9520b69b7102d242b&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3651393275%2C760516190%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=4d988b8c714247296bc2f03a2085afab&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3558994245%2C3926236555%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502968&di=788a9695190a5593a9557fc6bb8bbf97&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3703786357%2C853121273%26fm%3D179%2